# Performance Optimization Rules

## Animation Guidelines
- **AVOID heavy animations** - Use static elements instead of complex motion animations
- **Minimize framer-motion usage** - Replace motion.div with regular divs when possible
- **Remove auto-rotating carousels** - Use static displays for better performance
- **Simplify transitions** - Keep duration under 300ms for hover effects

## Component Optimization
- **Remove unused imports** - Clean up motion, useRef, useEffect when not needed
- **Use static components** - Replace AnimatedNumber with static displays
- **Minimize useEffect hooks** - Remove unnecessary animation intervals
- **Delete unused files** - Remove components like IntegrationSlideshow when no longer used

## Code Structure
- **Keep components lightweight** - Focus on functionality over visual effects
- **Optimize for mobile** - Prioritize performance on lower-end devices
- **Reduce bundle size** - Remove heavy animation libraries when possible